error.message: Parameter $entityQuery of method Drupal\image_export_import\EntitySaveHelper::__construct() has typehint with deprecated class Drupal\Core\Entity\Query\QueryFactory. Deprecated in drupal:8.3.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityStorageInterface::getQuery() or \Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityStorageInterface::getAggregateQuery() instead.
Call to deprecated function file_delete(). Deprecated in drupal:8.7.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\Entity\EntityStorageInterface::delete() instead.
Call to deprecated constant FILE_EXISTS_RENAME: Deprecated in drupal:8.7.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\File\FileSystemInterface::EXISTS_RENAME.
Call to deprecated function drupal_set_message(). Deprecated in drupal:8.5.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\Messenger\MessengerInterface::addMessage() instead.
Call to deprecated function drupal_set_message(). Deprecated in drupal:8.5.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Use \Drupal\Core\Messenger\MessengerInterface::addMessage() instead.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to image_export_import.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
